# All tests are deterministic. They pass only if the implementation correctly
# propagates whatever value is stored in the @export variable into the
# corresponding Camera2D property, with no clamping, guarding, or defaulting
# performed by the script itself (since SPEC-39 mandates unconditional assignment
# and SPEC-42 explicitly states "No script validation of limit relationships").
